description: A retrospective analysis of proteomics data from nine different human tissues, to understand the inter-individual and inter-tissue variability in protein expression. We used the data to build robust classifiers to predict the tissue of origin.

keywords.name: submitter keyword
keywords.value: machine learning, human proteome, tissue classification

terms.value: Kushner IK, Clair G, Purvine SO, Lee JY, Adkins JN, Payne SH. Individual Variability of Protein Expression in Human Tissues. J Proteome Res. 2018

title: Individual variability of protein expression in human tissues
